Package: rcicrdiagnostics
Title: Data-Quality Diagnostics for Reverse Correlation Experiments
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Manuel", "Oliveira",
           email = "manuel.olivethree@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A systematic battery of data-quality checks for reverse
    correlation experiments. Supports both the standard two-image
    forced-choice (2IFC) pipeline via the 'rcicr' package and the
    Brief-RC pipeline (Schmitz et al., 2024) that uses direct noise
    matrix multiplication. Designed to be run before computing
    classification images or information values so that silent
    data-processing errors are caught early.
